        <p>Cabinet at 12°F, should be at 0°F. Condenser visibly loaded with restaurant kitchen grease. 45-minute clean, recovery to 2°F within 2 hours. Set restaurant on quarterly PM contract. Total: $120 plus 45 minutes labor = $200 all-in.</p>
